{"title":"Helping older people maintain a healthy diet: a review of what works","public_updated_at":"2017-02-02T11:25:18Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<p>Malnutrition in older people can have a significant impact on their health and social care needs. Identifying and treating malnutrition is an important preventative measure that will reduce demands on health and care services.</p>\n\n<p>This review of evidence looks at ‘what works’ in supporting older people to maintain a healthy diet and reduce the risk of malnutrition.</p>\n\n<p>The information and examples of promising practice are intended to help those working in older people’s health, particularly nutrition, and local decision makers.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2017-02-02T11:25:18.000+00:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1897802\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/publications/helping-older-people-maintain-a-healthy-diet-a-review-of-what-works/helping-older-people-maintain-a-healthy-diet-a-review-of-what-works\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/assets/pub-cover-html-b0465911e56983d98c70f0e25fba24bc206d37e8c83d4addf6421dcf6022c6cd.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/publications/helping-older-people-maintain-a-healthy-diet-a-review-of-what-works/helping-older-people-maintain-a-healthy-diet-a-review-of-what-works\">Helping older people maintain a healthy diet: A review of what works </a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"references\">\n          Ref: <span class=\"unique_reference\">PHE publications gateway number: 2016567</span>\n        </span>\n        <span class=\"type\">HTML</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n  </div>\n</section>"],"emphasised_organisations":["1343f283-19e9-4fbb-86b1-58c7549d874b"],"political":false,"government":{"title":"2015 Cons